Prerequisite: BIOEE 1610. Priority for enrollment will be given to biological sciences majors in the EEB program of study. Limited to 22 students. One weekend field trip.
Recommended prerequisite: BIOEE 2740. S-U grades by permission only.

Prerequisite: BIOEE 1610 or permission of instructor. One Saturday field trip. The class is now closed to enrollment.

This would affect Dean's List eligibility but not eligibility for graduating with distinction.
